('garoupa_recheada_bissau_guinean', 'Garoupa Recheada', 228, 26.4, 6.4, 10.8, 1.0, 1.8, 250, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['garoupa recheada', 'stuffed grouper', 'garoupa recheada com gambas'], 'seafood', NULL, 1, 'GW', 'Stuffed grouper with shrimp, herbs, and tomato; grouper is Guinea-Bissau''s premium reef fish and stuffing it with shellfish creates a celebrated festive dish.', TRUE),
