('caldo_de_peixe_fresco_bissau_guinean', 'Caldo de Peixe Fresco', 108, 11.8, 7.4, 2.8, 1.2, 2.4, 350, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['caldo de peixe fresco', 'fresh fish broth', 'caldo de cabeça de peixe'], 'soup', NULL, 1, 'GW', 'Light fresh fish broth made from the bones and head of the catch-of-the-day; prepared by fishers'' families immediately after landing, using every part of the fish.', TRUE),
