('inhame_cozido_bissau_guinean', 'Inhame Cozido', 118, 1.5, 27.9, 0.2, 4.1, 0.5, 150, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['inhame cozido', 'boiled yam', 'yam cozido'], 'side dishes', NULL, 1, 'GW', 'Boiled yam (Dioscorea species) served as a starchy accompaniment to sauces and stews. Yam cultivation has deep roots in West African food traditions.', TRUE),
