('caldo_de_mancarra_bissau_guinean', 'Caldo de Mancarra', 165, 7.5, 12.0, 11.5, 2.8, 3.5, 200, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['caldo de mancarra', 'peanut soup', 'soupe d''arachide', 'mancarra broth'], 'traditional', NULL, 1, 'GW', 'Rich peanut broth soup, a dish central to Guinean identity. Mancarra (peanut) is the country''s most economically important crop and permeates the national cuisine.', TRUE),
