('ovo_cozido_com_molho_de_tomate_bissau_guinean', 'Ovo Cozido com Molho de Tomate', 162, 12.0, 5.5, 10.5, 1.0, 3.5, 150, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['ovo cozido com molho de tomate', 'eggs in tomato sauce', 'ovos no molho de tomate'], 'egg dishes', NULL, 1, 'GW', 'Hard-boiled eggs served in a spiced tomato sauce, a common preparation in urban Guinea-Bissau. The tomato sauce elevates simple boiled eggs to a full side dish.', TRUE),
